pipeline_summary.name: retail_inventory_reconciliation
pipeline_summary.description: Retail inventory reconciliation pipeline implementing a fanout fanin pattern across four warehouse systems.

components.name: Fetch Warehouse CSV
components.description: Retrieves inventory CSV files from each warehouse management system (north, south, east, west) via API calls.

upstream_policy.description: No upstream dependencies; runs at schedule start.

connections.purpose: Access warehouse management system for each region

components.name: Normalize Warehouse SKUs
components.description: Standardizes SKU formats in each warehouse's inventory CSV to a common schema.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after the corresponding fetch task has succeeded for the same region.

connections.purpose: Read raw CSVs and write normalized CSVs

components.name: Reconcile All Inventories
components.description: Consolidates normalized inventory files from all regions and identifies SKU discrepancies.

upstream_policy.description: Executes after all four normalization tasks have completed successfully.

connections.purpose: Read normalized CSVs and write discrepancy report

components.name: Generate Final Reconciliation Report
components.description: Creates a final PDF report summarizing inventory discrepancies across all warehouses.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after the reconciliation task finishes successfully.

connections.purpose: Read discrepancy CSV and write final PDF report

description.default: Retail inventory reconciliation pipeline implementing a fanout fanin pattern across four warehouse systems.

depends_on_past.description: Whether execution depends on previous run success

warehouse_id.description: Identifier of the warehouse region to fetch data from

csv_file.description: Path or name of the CSV file to normalize
